                <html:p><fr:link href="/schm-R3J8/" title="Affine schemes of free distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-R3J8/" display-uri="schm-R3J8" type="local">Affine schemes of free distributive lattices</fr:link> are always <fr:link href="/schm-HKT4/" title="Irreducible schemes" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-HKT4/" display-uri="schm-HKT4" type="local">irreducible</fr:link>, since free distributive lattices are always <fr:link href="/idem-comm-487K/" title="Integral distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-487K/" display-uri="idem-comm-487K" type="local">integral</fr:link>.
