            <fr:title text="Integral distributive lattices">Integral distributive lattices</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  A distributive lattice <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is <html:em>integral</html:em> if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D^{\mathrm {op}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/idem-comm-75C1/" title="Local distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-75C1/" display-uri="idem-comm-75C1" type="local">local</fr:link>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
